    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"journey\" feels more like a slow crawl through a dark hallway with no exit. if the end is just silence and zero meaning, why is it better to drag it out than to just face the nothingness now? it feels like fighting a battle that was lost before it even started.",
